Package: encodeUtils
Type: Package
Title: Query and Retrieve ENCODE Portal Metadata and Files
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Zoheb",
    family = "Khan",
    email = "zohebkhan600@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0266-8886")
    )
Description: Provides an R interface for querying ENCODE Portal metadata and
    working with files attached to ENCODE experiments. The package helps users
    search for datasets, list and select files, inspect planned downloads, read
    supported local files, and record reproducibility manifests. It is designed
    for scripted, accession-aware workflows that need to find and retrieve
    high-throughput sequencing data without leaving R.
